<SLUG> BC-DIETITIAN25-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Effects of resveratrol are still unclear
 &HT;    By Karen Collins
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   AUSTIN, Texas _
</P>
<P>
   Q: Is the resveratrol found in wine available in any other
foods?
</P>
<P>
   A: Resveratrol is a naturally occurring substance found mainly
