   GLASS-COLUMN _ WASHINGTON _ John McCain has pursued the need to
ban soft money as his political Holy Grail. On his return from Bora
Bora, the senator called on both presidential candidates to eschew
soft money. And Gore has issued his own separate challenge to Bush
along those lines. (Andy Glass is a columnist for Cox News Service
in the Washington bureau.) MOVED THURSDAY FOR SUNDAY.
