be anti-climactic because acting President Vladimir Putin is the
runaway victor. We take a good look at what the United States and
the West may expect from the new guy with access to the launch
codes for the world's second largest nuclear arsenal. (Coker,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). FOR SUNDAY
