unstoppable swell _ the result can be as transporting and
illuminating as the muddiest trek through Bergman. Yes, human
existence is fraught with grief and ends with death and the good
lord knows what's next. Too true, too true; we've seen it on bumper
stickers (``Life's a __ and then you die'') and in multiple
screenings of ``The Seventh Seal.''
</P>
<P>
   Sometimes, a great film comes along that reminds us,
beautifully, of our mortality. Sometimes, a great film comes along
that doesn't. Oscar or no Oscar, three cheers for the ones that
don't.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-03-24-00 1327EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
