   CAMPUS-FOR-SALE &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ If the multimillion-dollar auction doesn't work out,
maybe Ambassador University can be offered as an ultra-extravagant
gift in the Neiman Marcus Christmas catalog. On April 4, the
Worldwide Church of God will seek a Texas-size bid for the
Texas-size property _ a leafy, 2,200-acre former university campus
that includes a golf course, landing strip, radio station and
46-acre lake. By Bill Hanna. Story will move in ``a'' general news
category. &QL; 
