<P>
   COXNET INSIDE NASCAR 0324: ROBERT YATES, MASTER ENGINE BUILDER _
Modifying a 1957 Chevy as a teen-ager gave Robert Yates the
foundation to become a top NASCAR engine builder. (Minter, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   ON THE RISE _ A look at who's hot and who's not on the NASCAR
circuit. (Carvell, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   MAKING HEADLINES _ A summary of NASCAR's top stories. (Carvell,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
