   G CARSON CUNNINGHAM 6-1 188 JR
</P>
<P>
   Key stats: Averaged 10.8 points, 4.2 assists
</P>
<P>
   C GREG MCQUAY 6-7 220 SR
</P>
<P>
   Key stats: Averages 8.1 points, 5.3 rebounds
</P>
