3.1 assists G JON BRYANT 6-2 185 SR Key stat: Averages 7.9 points,
1.2 assists per game F ANDY KOWSKE 6-8 230 JR Key stats: Averages
9.3 points, 6.4 rebounds C MARK VERSHAW 6-9 235 JR Key stat:
Averages 12.2 points, 4.2 rebounds F MAURICE LINTON 6-8 215 JR Key
stat: Averages 4.5 points, 2.8 rebounds
