<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-24 22:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7468 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-BKC-NCAA-MIDWEST-NYT &LR;      03-24 0756
