<HEADLINE>
BROKER ADMITS SELLING DRUGS ON FLOOR OF STOCK EXCHANGE 
</HEADLINE>
  (Eds., also filed in ``a'' category) 
(mk) 
 By JULIAN E. BARNES   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ Shares of Time Warner and Citigroup are among the
typical things bought and sold at the New York Stock Exchange. But
