u s BC-BKN-NCAA-WEST-NYT &LR;      03-24 0616
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BKN-NCAA-WEST-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A MATCHUP OF HARD KNOCKS ON HARDWOOD 
</HEADLINE>
  (lh) 
 By TOM SPOUSTA   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
